    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, drain your <strong>king prawns</strong></p><p>Add your <strong>ground smoked paprika</strong> to a plate with a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Mix everything together, then add the <strong>drained</strong> <strong>king prawns</strong> to the plate and turn them several times until they're fully coated – these are your<strong> paprika king prawns</strong></p>",
